  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uh oh, it seems your delivery bike got stolen. No worries, you've got a spare unicycle that you can use instead. Navigate the dense cityscapes and make sure your deliveries are on time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/aebe2f45c504ba87f6037ca955682b63.webp?t=1755277236\" width=600 height=50 /></span>You'll have to navigate the tricky cityscape, what architect did they allow to design this place!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/09b11c97d8aa3d4ee69543bba971c648.poster.avif?t=1755277236\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/09b11c97d8aa3d4ee69543bba971c648.webm?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/09b11c97d8aa3d4ee69543bba971c648.mp4?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/8ac2ab93454b5f5e281eec42bf81fb3d.webp?t=1755277236\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Go and deliver pizzas with 1-4 delivery drivers and compete against each other. The first person to deliver gets the biggest tip after all...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/22a12e07d731af07252c626f16646009.poster.avif?t=1755277236\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/22a12e07d731af07252c626f16646009.webm?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/22a12e07d731af07252c626f16646009.mp4?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/dd6c55354fee5de30663c290d6791f62.webp?t=1755277236\" width=600 height=50 /></span>- Online leaderboards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Controller support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Pimp your unicycle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A lot of rage</p>",
